Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:48.36,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(710,1070)\shad3}Woom　镜中照出的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:52.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(710,1070)\shad3}Woom　也挺美丽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:55.99,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(710,1070)\shad3}感觉很不错. . .
